Nativeness Q parameter

Available options

  • structure structure abcd.pdb:5:A,28,59
    Reference structure is in the PDB file abcd.pdb, model 5, chain A, residues index labels 28 through 59 in that file. The NativenessQ Observable obeys the same rules for selecting parts of PDB files as prf::ProteinRMSD. The rules are described in ProFASi PDB handling: Selections and Filters .
  • alt_crd: alt_crd occupancy
    In case an alternative atom entries are found in a pdb file, this command sets the policy to be adopted. The value "occupancy" ensures the line with the highest occupancy value is used. Other possible policies are "first" and "last".
    See also:
    prf::NativenessQ
